      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（ⅢXは、I-UNITYで琴乃達と戦った相手だ）\n（決勝でギリギリ、サニピが勝った訳だけど……）",
      "startTime": 17.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（いろいろあったとはいえ負けた相手と）\n（同じ事務所に入るのは複雑だろうな）",
      "startTime": 24.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが、私達のマネジメントを\n担当して下さると三枝さんからうかがいましたが……",
      "startTime": 29.2666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "自分達のマネジメントは自分で出来ますから\n面倒を見ていただく必要はありません",
      "startTime": 35.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "建前上、マネージャーが必要だとは分かりますけど……\nくれぐれも、余計な口出しはしないようお願いします",
      "startTime": 43.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyoconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyoconference-00-noon"
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "（……予想はしてたけど、この人のマネージャーを）\n（務めるのは、思った以上の難題だな……）",
      "startTime": 50.7581726074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
