      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01/sud_vo_adv_card_mhk_01_01-mhk017.m4a",
      "text": "……失礼します\nロッカーから、予備を取って来ますので",
      "startTime": 147.4666666667,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_down-01.m4a",
